    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Interactive tables in Quarto\"\nformat: html\n---\n\nYou can create complex data visualization with R and Quarto, but there may be times when you just want to show your table of data in a way that is useful to readers. There are a number of ways to format tables. This page provides a preview of what you can do with tables in Quarto.\n\nIf you want a nicely formatted static table, look at the [gt package](https://gt.rstudio.com). The documentation for the package is very thorough and provides many examples.\n\nA minimally interactive option is `rmarkdown::paged_table()`, which can be chosen as the default table output within the [`df-print` option in Quarto's YAML](https://quarto.org/docs/computations/r.html#data-frames). But you can get even fancier with either the [DT package](https://rstudio.github.io/DT/) or [reactable](https://glin.github.io/reactable/).\n\n## Examples\nLet's show examples using the movements of two sibling groups at the end of the 16th century.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nlibrary(tidyverse)\nlibrary(DT)\nlibrary(reactable)\n```\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nmovements <- read_csv(\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jessesadler/vt5444s26/refs/heads/main/datasets/movements.csv\")\n```\n:::\n\n\n### Regular tibble output\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nmovements\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}\n\n```\n# A tibble: 74 × 3\n   person                 place     date      \n   <chr>                  <chr>     <date>    \n 1 Andries van der Meulen Antwerp   1584-07-01\n 2 Andries van der Meulen Bremen    1585-09-01\n 3 Anna van der Meulen    Cologne   1584-07-01\n 4 Anna van der Meulen    Bremen    1588-06-01\n 5 Anna van der Meulen    Stade     1588-08-01\n 6 Anna van der Meulen    Bremen    1592-03-01\n 7 Sara van der Meulen    Antwerp   1584-07-01\n 8 Sara van der Meulen    Bremen    1585-09-01\n 9 Sara van der Meulen    Frankfurt 1586-03-01\n10 Sara van der Meulen    Cologne   1586-05-01\n# ℹ 64 more rows\n```\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n### RMarkdown paged\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nrmarkdown::paged_table(movements)\n```\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<div data-pagedtable=\"false\">\n  <script data-pagedtable-source type=\"application/json\">\n{\"columns\":[{\"label\":[\"person\"],\"name\":[1],\"type\":[\"chr\"],\"align\":[\"left\"]},{\"label\":[\"place\"],\"name\":[2],\"type\":[\"chr\"],\"align\":[\"left\"]},{\"label\":[\"date\"],\"name\":[3],\"type\":[\"date\"],\"align\":[\"right\"]}],\"data\":[{\"1\":\"Andries van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Andries van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Bremen\",\"3\":\"1585-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Cologne\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Bremen\",\"3\":\"1588-06-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Stade\",\"3\":\"1588-08-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Bremen\",\"3\":\"1592-03-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Bremen\",\"3\":\"1585-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Frankfurt\",\"3\":\"1586-03-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Cologne\",\"3\":\"1586-05-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Frankfurt\",\"3\":\"1589-06-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Bremen\",\"3\":\"1592-03-01\"},{\"1\":\"Sara van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Utrecht\",\"3\":\"1598-06-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Leiden\",\"3\":\"1584-11-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Geertruidenberg\",\"3\":\"1585-11-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Leiden\",\"3\":\"1586-04-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1586-05-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Leiden\",\"3\":\"1586-08-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1596-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jan della Faille\",\"2\":\"Leiden\",\"3\":\"1596-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Marten della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Marten della Faille\",\"2\":\"Bergen op Zoom\",\"3\":\"1587-08-01\"},{\"1\":\"Marten della Faille\",\"2\":\"The Hague\",\"3\":\"1588-02-01\"},{\"1\":\"Marten della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1588-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Carlo della Faille\",\"2\":\"Dordrecht\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Carlo della Faille\",\"2\":\"Zevenbergen\",\"3\":\"1592-01-01\"},{\"1\":\"Carlo della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1595-11-01\"},{\"1\":\"Carlo della Faille\",\"2\":\"Brussels\",\"3\":\"1596-01-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Anna della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1585-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Dordrecht\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1585-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Brussels\",\"3\":\"1586-01-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1593-09-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Amsterdam\",\"3\":\"1596-01-01\"},{\"1\":\"Steven della Faille\",\"2\":\"Utrecht\",\"3\":\"1600-01-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"Hamburg\",\"3\":\"1585-10-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"Emden\",\"3\":\"1585-11-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1585-12-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"The Hague\",\"3\":\"1586-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"London\",\"3\":\"1586-08-01\"},{\"1\":\"Jacques della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1587-05-01\"},{\"1\":\"Hester della Faille\",\"2\":\"Haarlem\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Daniel van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Antwerp\",\"3\":\"1584-07-01\"},{\"1\":\"Daniel van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Middelburg\",\"3\":\"1584-08-01\"},{\"1\":\"Daniel van der Meulen\",\"2\":\"Delft\",\"3\":\"1584-09-01\"},